{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal for over 18s to engage in sexual activity with under 18s",
        "additional_details": "It is currently legal for anyone over 18 to have sexual contact with a 16 or 17 year-old - unless they are in a 'position of trust' and the child is in their care. That adult could be a \u2019family friend\u2019 who has the trust of a child\u2019s parents/carers and has known the child their whole life.",
        "background": "We want to prevent sexual exploitation of 16-17 year olds, recognising young people at this age are vulnerable to grooming & exploitation by adults. This petition asks the UK govt. to better protect 16-17 year olds by making it illegal for adults to engage in sexual activity with any under 18s.",
